@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qvdeuc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.44 - v0 + 0.79) + wp.sin(v0 + 0.63)))
    v1 = ((0.99 * wp.cos(v1 + 0.09)) - wp.exp((v1 + 0.37 * v0 + 0.63)))
    tmp = wp.cos(((v1 + 0.99 - v2 + 0.95) + 0.39))
    v0 = wp.abs((0.55 * wp.cos(v0 + 0.53)))
    tmp = (0.45 + wp.cos((v1 + 0.40 * tmp + 0.41)))
    v0 = 0.48
    v2 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
